| TASK-CANCEL-ATOMICITY-001 | FR-012 / AC-012 / AC-E015 | repaired | `npm run test:api` 断言取消状态更新必须携带原 `status` 与 `attemptNo` CAS 条件，旧 PENDING 取消快照不能覆盖已推进到 EXECUTING 的任务；`npm run test:worker` 断言旧 EXECUTING 取消快照不能覆盖 FAILED retry 后递增出的新 `attemptNo`。同一轮继续保留 PENDING cancel、EXECUTING 批次边界 cancel 与 FAILED retry 既有状态机证据 | local/Docker MySQL API + worker evidence；CAS miss 收口为未更新或非法状态，不声明外部生产 MySQL evidence |

